{"tid":1461103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一群TVB員工致香港人的公開信","createTime":"2019-08-13T06:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T13:17:17.000Z","uid":282218,"like":296,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"dc3137995e8da5e261dceafbc6fd2afadc1161e4","tid":1461103,"uid":282218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:15:26.000Z","msg":"致香港人：<br />\n<br />\n大家好，我們是一群電視廣播有限公司（以下稱TVB）的現職員工。 <br />\n<br />\nTVB陪伴香港人逾半世紀，除了有劇集和綜藝節目去娛樂大眾，無綫新聞向來報道社會大事，秉承「無綫新聞，事事關心」的精神，成為香港歷史的記錄者。惟政府提出修訂《逃犯條例》演變成社會嚴重撕裂，警民衝突不斷升溫，我們與巿民一樣感到極度痛心；而作為TVB員工，卻同時為新聞部的表現感到不安。<br />\n <br />\n眼見無綫新聞不斷被外界質疑自我審查、偏頗、成為政權傳聲筒等等，連帶其他員工亦因此而在工作上被質疑其專業操守，作為熱愛TVB的員工感到非常難過憂心。有人曾把TVB報道修例正反意見的篇幅作出統計，結果是贊成修例的篇幅遠多於反修例，而畫面更集中於示威者的暴力行為，更遑論追尋事實根本，這讓巿民覺得報道有導向之嫌。譴責暴力容易，但尋出暴力根源才能治本。<br />\n <br />\n我們認為香港撕裂至此，責任全在林鄭月娥及其班子，政府必須正式回應民間訴求，包括撤回條例及成立獨立調查委員會等，局亂才有望稍息。我們呼籲公司管理層確實切行作為媒體的職責，是為政府的監察者而非維穩者，認清新聞是為「香港」而報道，並非為「政府」而發聲，真實反映社會聲音。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我們將會與巿民一同密切監察無綫新聞的報道內容，期望能回歸報道真實民情的初心。</span><br />\n<br />\n口號如下：<br />\n「捍衛新聞自由、彰顯社會公義！<br />\n堅守專業操守、不作政府喉舌！」<br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油！<br />\n<br />\n一群熱愛香港，熱愛電視行業的工作者上<br />\n<br />\n／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／<br />\n歡迎TVB員工繼續發送員工證<br />\ntelegram&gt;&gt;&gt; <a href=\"https://t.me/StopCCTVB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FStopCCTVB&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=8ccfa1f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/StopCCTVB</a><br />\nemail&gt;&gt;&gt; stopcctvb@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n目前已有過百員工聯署<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDjqsra.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDjqsra.jpg&h=800b9123&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d4833cf482df4b0b96e2be924626b89d75562b1","tid":1461103,"uid":294974,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:16:21.000Z","msg":"只要同路就係朋友，唔理背景<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"6943baa726606097455330395f0bebca1806edec","tid":1461103,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:17:19.000Z","msg":"P牌幫你用念力推po"},{"pid":"7c5df5bcb802b4275780d88948ab1473b0f5206c","tid":1461103,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:17:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f43fbbe6d7b639c0674234ac934450536ddbde8","tid":1461103,"uid":282218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:22:26.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"68a7fce9fd146d7797b1253cd6fa5dfbdb7f7bf7","tid":1461103,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:24:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2dd4010496a93671ac7d62c706e3a36bb273e8bf","tid":1461103,"uid":159990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:25:24.000Z","msg":"tvb都有好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e015c49a1e5cb23e24f132173c58d38df02bb374","tid":1461103,"uid":4151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0aaf309ff9c0386a90fada45aa60a642b42c48","tid":1461103,"uid":51801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173732db6031e707466ac74e29bfdd8a84e865ed","tid":1461103,"uid":204891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:31:19.000Z","msg":"